INUMBER 981
NAME 182
SHIELD
WEIGHT 10
VOLUME 8
PARAMETER1 15
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Five majestic dragons in flight gaze out at you from the face of the shield.
Each dragon has been placed in such a way that any light captures all of them
at the same moment, causing a beautiful rainbow to shine over the entire
shield. Each individual scale has been polished to a high lustre and causes
the entire shield to be viewed as one that resonates with unearthly beauty.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE hornsby
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  ECHO PLAYER A melodious, bass voice fills your mind, "Know mortal that you now posess the shield of Takleron, Dragon Friend. The mightiest of heroes Takleron earned the eternal gratitude of Dragons for his brave rescue of a female's clutch of eggs."
  ECHO PLAYER "Harken to me as I tell you of Takleron! In ancient times the eggs of dragons were highly sought by those who considered themselves mighty workers of magic, for there is power in our young. One such fell sorceror, named Eyaniek, stole the eggs of a dragoness. Takleron, being an honorable warrior, heard of this foul deed."
  ECHO PLAYER "Takleron journeyed to the black tower of this evil sorceror and bested both traps and beasts to regain the dragon eggs. When he returned the dragons rejoiced, for we do not have many young. In thanks, this shield was created. Let me tell you of its making...."
  ECHO PLAYER "Dragons formed a circle and created a blaze in the center of the ring with the magical fire that flows from all dragons when they wish. They fed this fire with their breath, not letting it die until the ritual was completed."
  ECHO PLAYER "Mor'Tienh'Kolar, the Black Dragon, leaned forward and took a scale from his back. Placing the scale within the fire he said, "Those of my color do you honor, Takleron. I bind the art of healing into this, my scale."
  ECHO PLAYER "Qiur'Tovag, the White Dragon, stepped forth, her beauty evident for all. Gently placing a white scale into the fire she said, "Takleron, those of my tribe, do you honor. Our magics will grant you protection in battle."
  ECHO PLAYER "Jal'Khomar'Wento, the Red Dragon, stepped forth, flames licking around his scales. Ripping one of the scales from his back the mighty dragon placed it within the fire and intoned, "Let the magic of my brood always protect you from cold."
  ECHO PLAYER "Kalt'Snou'Terak, the Blue Dragon, lumbered forth, his age and wisdom causing all to fall before him. Placing a scale in the fire he said, "Let the protection of our magic always protect you from those who would seek to cause you harm with the element of fire."
  ECHO PLAYER "Finally, Dar'Thavian, the Green Dragon, flew forth and dropped a scale into the fire. Gazing imperiously around the chamber he intoned, "Takleron let the power of your magic grant you strength in combat."
  ECHO PLAYER The voice fades from your mind, leaving you with a feeling of awe.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
   ADD hornsby 1
  IFVAR hornsby < 26
   RANDOM dummy5 1 5 0
    IFVAR dummy5 = 1
      ECHO ALL %N rubs the shield...a glow covers it for a moment and then you see the image of the black dragon flow from the shield face and take form...the shimmering image of the black dragon gestures at %N and %N immediately looks better...the black dragon then slowly fades...
      SPELL 318 30
    ENDIF
     IFVAR dummy5 = 2
       ECHO ALL The image of the white dragon flows from %N's shield and takes shape over %N's head...the White Dragon image smiles gently at %N and then gestures at him before fading...
       SPELL 105 30
     ENDIF
      IFVAR dummy5 = 3
        ECHO ALL The majestic image of a Red Dragon flows from the shield and takes shape above %N..the Red Dragon breathes eldritch fire upon %N before slowly fading...
        SPELL 508 30
      ENDIF
       IFVAR dummy5 = 4
         ECHO ALL An icy field, twinkling with the intensity of diamonds caught in a brilliant light, covers %N, extending from the shimmering image of a Blue Dragon that appeared above %N's head...
         SPELL 507 30
       ENDIF
        IFVAR dummy5 = 5
          ECHO ALL The faint scent of spring hangs in the air as the image of the Green Dragon flows from %N's shield and takes form above him. The Green Dragon gestures at %N and then slowly fades away...
          SPELL 209 30
        ENDIF
   ENDIF
    IFVAR hornsby => 26
      ECHO PLAYER The shield remains quiescent, its power gone for the day.
      ECHO OTHERS %N rubs his shield.
    ENDIF
ENDIF
;
INUMBER 985
NAME 476
MISC
WEIGHT 1000
VOLUME 10
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  CLEARVERB
  RANDOM dummy2 1 4 0
   IFVAR dummy2 = 1
     ECHO PLAYER The painting shimmers until you are viewing the titanic battle against the Broodlord. You see the streets of Fayd where King Frederick leads a band against the inexorable tides of Ravagers and Nightsteeds. You see Duke Moonpie and Duchess Camorra, valiantly holding the front gate of Fayd against wave upon wave of evil creatures. You see the final minutes of the battle when the small band of heroes bravely defeated the superior numbers of enemies at the Town Square.
     ECHO OTHERS %N looks at the painting.
   ENDIF
    IFVAR dummy2 = 2
      ECHO PLAYER The painting shimmers until you are viewing the blazing metal hallways of a spaceship. Ferumbras stands facing the snarling visage of Siryx as a monotonous voice counts down the seconds until the ship will explode. You see Ferumbras gesture and then see Siryx encased in a blue force bubble. The final image is of a starship exploding against a background of deep space as a mechanoid named Endir skilfully pilots the ship containing the heroes of FAyd from the scene.
      ECHO OTHERS %N looks at the painting.
    ENDIF
     IFVAR dummy2 = 3
       ECHO PLAYER The painting shimmers until you are viewing Kai and his personal battle against Loup Garou. You see Kai mouth the true name of the evil werewolf, causing Loup Garou to shrink back and finally fade...
       ECHO OTHERS %N looks at the painting.
     ENDIF
      IFVAR dummy2 = 4
        ECHO PLAYER The painting shimmers until you see a beautiful golden-haired woman, dressed in golden armor, fighting minions of darkness deep within the catacombs. Her skill is awe-inspiring and her bravery exemplary, but as you realize that you are watching Princess Solaria you see a single black sword break through her defenses causing an end to young Princesses life...
        ECHO OTHERS %N looks at the painting.
      ENDIF
ENDIF
