INUMBER 1541
NAME 1441
MISC
WEIGHT 5
VOLUME 2
WORN_DON
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
The heartstone pulses slightly with a myriad of colors. Taken from the
core of Andor this stone is filled with unpredictable power. For good or
ill you will never know, for the power of the earth runs deep and is
beyond the ken, or control, of mortals.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB WEAR -1
  ECHO PLAYER As you place the heartstone onto your body you feel it graft itself onto your skin. Earthpower courses through you and you are illuminated in its glow!
  ECHO OTHERS The heartstone sinks into %N's skin, embedding itself into %h chest. The blinding light of earthpower outlines %N for a moment and then fades.
  APPEAR The heartstone pulses slightly, embedded in the center of %N's chest.
ENDIF
IFVERB REMOVE -1
  ECHO PLAYER The heartstone comes free with a loud, popping sound.
  ECHO OTHERS %N wrenches the heartstone from %h chest.
  APPEAR A slightly scorched area is in the center of %N's chest.
  CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
 IFITEM -1 WORN
 IFVAR INTNUM40 = 6
 SUBITEMVAL -1 5 1
 IFVAR ITEMVAL5 > 0
  RANDOM DUMMY1 1 10 0
    IFVAR DUMMY1 < 4
      ECHO PLAYER More power than you can handle burns through your body!
      ECHO OTHERS Violent earthpower flares through %N's body causing %i to scream in pain!
      SPELL 315 10
    ENDIF
    IFVAR DUMMY1 = 4
      ECHO PLAYER The heartstone emits a glowing protective field around your body.
      ECHO OTHERS A glowing, white protective field emanates from %N and covers %h body.
      SPELL 102 30
    ENDIF
    IFVAR dummy1 => 5
      IFVAR dummy1 =< 8
      ECHO PLAYER You feel the earthpower flow through your body soothing and healing your injuries.
      ECHO OTHERS %N's life vitality is restored by the power of earth magic.
      SPELL 318 20
    ENDIF
    ENDIF
    IFVAR dummy1 => 9
       ECHO PLAYER The flow of magic from the heartstone revitalizes you!
       ECHO OTHERS %N's is revitalized by the flow of power from the heartstone!
       SPELL 335 10
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 0
    ECHO PLAYER The power of the heartstone has been stilled.
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
