INUMBER 1536
NAME 1438
MISC
WEIGHT 2
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE BRITTLE
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Alskar is a cute and cuddly little ball of light brown, wrinkly fur. His
little tail whips about in an excited, happy frenzy as he looks adoringly
up at you. His oversized little paws bat affectionately at anything that
crosses his path. Big, soulful eyes look up at you, expressing total
love and trust for you.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB RUB -1
  ECHO ALL Alskar sways from side to side, his little face aglow with pleasure as %N rubs his back.
ENDIF
IFVERB CARESS -1
  ECHO ALL The little legs of the Alskar move in a delighted fashion as %N scratches his stomach.
ENDIF
IFVERB KISS -1
  ECHO ALL Alskar yips with pleasure as %N kisses him, pushing his little head against %N and affectionately licking %h face.
ENDIF
IFVERB HUG -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL Alskar disappears into %N's arms, only his little tail, wagging excitedly, and a cute little nose, pressed against %N's chin, are visible.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL %N rolls a ball along the floor, with an excited yip, Alskar skids after it, his whole backside swaying as his tail wags furiously with excitement. Skidding to a stop, his cute paws splayed out on the floor, just past the ball, he picks it up in his mouth and proudly brings it back to %N, jumping affectionately into %h lap and presenting the ball.
ENDIF
