This small hallway runs through the thick outer walls surrounding the
Palace grounds. Burning torches cast a light around the area, outlining
the white marble arch on the west wall that leads into a larger room.
A stone arch to the north leads onto the Palace grounds and a large
mirmach door to the south leads back out to Park Avenue.
