NUMBER 5
NAME Heroes Rest, courtyard
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
A wide cobblestoned courtyard spreads out from a centrally located
fountain that gurgles happily with flowing water. Comfortable benches
sit under the drooping willow trees that line the edges of the courtyard,
offering weary travellers a chance to rest in the shade. Narrow paths
run from the edges of the square heading into a profusion of lush
greenery that arc over the paths to form natural tunnels. The songs of
brightly colored birds can be heard from the surrounding treetops their
voices adding a quiet serenity to the peaceful surroundings, combining
with the bubbling water from the fountain to soothe nerves and ease
troubled minds with the natural harmony of nature. To the south, resting
in the shade of large oak trees sits a cozy-looking two story wooden
building.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 6
EXIT S 7
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=784 ADJ2=407 VAL2=516
ITEM 1 197 ADJ1=187
EXTEND 1 with flecks of pink running through its surface
PUT 1 198 VAL2=100
ITEM 2 204 ADJ1=294 ADJ2=355
ITEM 3 304
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Slightly smaller than the fountain in Fayd this bubbling pool of
enthusiasm radiates with good cheer and happiness as evidenced by
the shimmering glow of its water. The pink streaks running through
its white marble surface are subdued but still colorful enough to
add to the atmosphere of joy the little fountain exudes. A small
wooden sign sits next to the fountain.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 2
       "NYMPH SHOW!!!"
"Every day at five in the afternoon!!!"
"Nudge me at that time if I forget!!!"
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE monnymphshow
IFVERB RECALL -1
  ECHO PLAYER You look closely at the fountain and realize that its remarkably similar to the one in Fayd. As you think about the similarity a small voice whispers to you, "Yes, I'm the offspring of the fountain in Fayd! Thanks to the efforts of Nissa, who introduced my parents one night, I came to be! This is my first job as a fountain, and I hope that I'll do well!"
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks thoughtfully at the fountain.
ENDIF
IFVERB PUSH 1
  IFVAR TIM = 17
   IFVAR monnymphshow = 1
     ECHO PLAYER The nymph is already in the midst of her routine.
   ENDIF
     IFVAR monnymphshow ! 1
       ADD monnymphshow 1
       ECHO ALL Lyrical dance music starts up from the surrounding spots of nature, its pulsating beat loud and seductive...
       PLREVENT 2
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL Streamers of multi-colored light shoot from the bubbling fountain forming a backdrop of beautiful scenery against the cascading water....
       PLREVENT 1
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL Emerging from the center of the dazzling light display in the fountain is a diminutive, beautiful nymph...she curtsies low and smiles prettily at you...and then begins to move as the music swells around her...
       PLREVENT 2
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL The nymph gracefully twirls around her watery stage, her body moving slowly and sensuosly to the music that surrounds her...
       PLREVENT 2
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL As the music pulsates around her the nymph falls to her knees and slowly lowers her head in front of her, her arms outstretched towards you...her tiny body sways from side to side as she starts to rise...
       PLREVENT 2
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL The nymph's hands slide slowly up her legs, then her body as dazzling, gold sparkled water falls over her form, making her transparent dress cling to her every curve...
       PLREVENT 1
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL As her hands reach her head the nymph leaps from her kneeling position to land nimbly on her feet...pirouetting around she casts glittering silver drops of water around the area...
       PLREVENT 2
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL The nymph spins rapidly as the music reaches a crescendo, her dress flying everywhere and exposing tantalizing views of smooth skin, until the last high note is reached and she suddenly stops! Her face flushed and panting slightly the nymph curtsies and then fades back into the water as the music does a final bump and grind before fading.
       EQUAL monnymphshow 0
     ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
