      ECHO ALL %N bows before the statue and raises %h hands. A glow surrounds %N and then the statue. A voice booms, "Let the mists of peace fill this spot until the truth is found." You feel a sense of calm wash over you.
    ENDIF
     IFVAR mondelanore = 2
       ECHO ALL %N gestures and intones, "Praise Ordanin, Bringer of Justice". The glow leaves the statue and you feel the sense of calm pass.
       EQUAL mondelanore 0
     ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
